{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 82126, "create_time": 1650527517, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "埋到草莓地？", "timestamp": 1650527517}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 82130, "create_time": 1650527553, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "像是柯南里故事", "timestamp": 1650527553}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 82135, "create_time": 1650527660, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "门窗从里面锁住怎么进的屋。。", "timestamp": 1650527660}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 82138, "create_time": 1650527737, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "线索太少", "timestamp": 1650527737}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 82140, "create_time": 1650527866, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "百度了一下据说肢解之后放在了食物篮子里，感觉太扯了", "timestamp": 1650527866}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 82147, "create_time": 1650528045, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "这样的故事很无聊，无论是动机还是作案过程。一味追求古怪却不符合现实，如果只是想要钱没必要这么残忍。", "timestamp": 1650528045}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 82150, "create_time": 1650528165, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "这类故事也是柯南系列的共性，什么密室之类的好像罪犯把杀人当成艺术了。其实越是古怪的案件越是容易侦破", "timestamp": 1650528165}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 82152, "create_time": 1650528282, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "\n![](https://bafkreicyz5ltyqu5ykus7r47ofrq4xwom4qouuaasjwqbueu5huf5xiyuy.ipfs.hub.textile.io/?filename=Screenshot_2022-04-21-16-04-12-27_40deb401b9ffe8e1df2f1cc5ba480b12.jpg&filetype=image%2Fjpeg) [加载失败请点击此](https://t-hole.red/ipfs.html#bafkreicyz5ltyqu5ykus7r47ofrq4xwom4qouuaasjwqbueu5huf5xiyuy)\n\n---\n", "timestamp": 1650528282}], "create_time": 1650527313, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1650528282, "likenum": 4, "n_attentions": 4, "n_comments": 8, "pid": 29995, "poll": null, "reply": 8, "text": "亨利应一位富家独生女之邀，和她的堂姐以及堂姐的未婚夫（外科医生），4人一起到郊外的别墅野餐。\n\n小巧轻盈的富家女，双亲都已去世，由她继承了巨额家产。到达别墅后，他们在庭院的草地上野餐。\n他们帯了3个大篮子，内中装满食物。吃饱后，篮子就收到别墅中。\n亨利在与堂姐谈天时，富家女和外科医生一起进了别墅。好久也不见他们出来。堂姐进屋察看，发现里面空无一人。当亨利也想进屋时，外科医生从另一边的树林里出来了。他一身泥巴，在摘野草莓。亨利问他富家女在哪里，他说在屋里。然而当他们3人进屋去时，却无论如何也找不到富家女，而且门窗都是从里面锁住的。享利找来找去，只是在走廊上捡到一块防水布片。3人失望地将别墅收拾整齐，把大篮子放回车上，离开了。\n后来警察又进行了仔细的检查，只在浴室里看到了一点血迹。\n富家女到哪里去了呢？她被谋杀了吗？尸体呢？凶手又是谁呢？", "timestamp": 1650527313}}